{"tid":896462,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(我又挑戰真人電影) 今次係龍虎門，港產片呀，比下面啦","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:25:00.000Z","uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a71b35b9e69863eeea9fa9a2a0593c9cbc426706","tid":896462,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"繼上次挑戰真人KOF 之後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(我又挑戰左一套真人電影...KOF 拳王<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/876370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/876370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區)</span><br />\n<br />\n我見到Netflix 有龍虎門喎(2006)！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/044836_83f110b571374a65cbf29d78ed2e6bcd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F044836_83f110b571374a65cbf29d78ed2e6bcd.png&h=63e6b188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然睇過路人、鋼鍊、龍珠，睇過KOF真人<br />\n<br />\n當然唔可以唔支持下本土<br />\n<br />\n龍虎門本身故事都係本土<br />\n<br />\n我細個無錢買，亦都冇得睇<br />\n<br />\n所以算得上白紙一張咁睇套戲<br />\n<br />\n有幾場特別深刻<br />\n<br />\n戲中出現Nokia 已經令我驚訝又驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來黃小虎及其餘4名二打六響日本餐廳中左蒙汗藥<br />\n<br />\n膠龍帶一堆黑衣人個個都揸住刀黎劈友<br />\n<br />\n然後開打到matrix reloaded 無限Smith 咁<br />\n<br />\n最後竟然冇人死！連重傷都冇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n刀喎！中左蒙汗藥喎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我當你黃小龍黃小虎係主角威能...咁d二打六呢？<br />\n<br />\n去到兩兄弟上天台傾計<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/054206_3d66dbe7c8ea513b7b2adb3b11108a79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F054206_3d66dbe7c8ea513b7b2adb3b11108a79.png&h=d58f2f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Netflix唔比cap圖，唯有手機影mon)<br />\n<br />\n天台勁大風，佢地個髮型只能以慘不忍睹黎形容<br />\n<br />\n成場文戲變左笑片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFinal 打大boss<br />\n<br />\n黃小虎使出電光毒龍鑽<br />\n<br />\n點知火雲邪神竟然使出無敵風火輪完全反制⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n成套戲火雲邪神都戴住面罩，我懷疑佢係何金銀所扮⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後對上宇宙丹既降龍十八掌，打到仲勁過龍珠<br />\n<br />\n一招從天而降既掌法收尾更令我產生幻覺，以為自己睇緊功夫(2004)<br />\n<br />\n由於我未睇過漫畫，但我相信以上種種都係因為90分鐘時限無法完整呈現漫畫既故事所致<br />\n我仍然覺得宇宙丹既打鬥好有動感<br />\n希望本土既電影越做越好"},{"pid":"cebdbe7ef72c49f987fc6dbf216a555795f4d72b","tid":896462,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"下次我可能會睇bleach真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9617473c38f24337f3822507747b4ae9d2199b75","tid":896462,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"套龍虎門整體上都係膠<br />\n不過有幾幕打鬥幾好睇<br />\n開頭茶樓檸檬打卒仔真係SHOW到佢有苦練過"},{"pid":"05e5496f81316917facbbc0284f27001e864a0db","tid":896462,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9617473c38f24337f3822507747b4ae9d2199b75","tid":896462,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"套龍虎門整體上都係膠<br />\n不過有幾幕打鬥幾好睇<br />\n開頭茶樓檸檬打卒仔真係SHOW到佢有苦練過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"其實係，演員好，但劇本令人失望"},{"pid":"35f2111b269d578521f43c15ff209647dc196550","tid":896462,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05e5496f81316917facbbc0284f27001e864a0db","tid":896462,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9617473c38f24337f3822507747b4ae9d2199b75","tid":89